    "body": "I believe this is a duplicate of this [issue](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/3005). At the moment, state changes are not persisted between tests, which means changes to `block.timestamp` or `block.number` won't persist. You have already figured out the workaround for now which is to persist the state and warp/roll to it. See this [comment](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/4994#issuecomment-1618329347) for a more complete solution.",
